Create new Laravel project:
xampp\htdocs or wamp\www
 right click -> git bash here
In git:
>Laravel new projectName
Or
>composer create-project laravel/laravel projectName "6.*"
“6.*” is Laravel wanted version

>composer config -g repo.packagist composer https://packagist.org
 It forces composer to use https to download all resources

>Composer install
Install all packages in composer.json
>php artisan serv
run the project to open in browser

php artisan make:controller FirstController
php artisan route:list
php artisan make:controller controllerName --resource
composer require laravel/ui
php artisan ui vue --auth
npm install && npm run dev

php artisan migrate
note: to solve [varchar(191) not null] error, go to app->Providoers->AppServiceProvider.php and add Schema::defaultStringLength(191); to boot function

php artisan dump-autoload (run after each change in .env file
